1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,567
Men in the flesh, or
rather, in the hazard suit, I

2
00:00:04,568 --> 00:00:08,500
took the liberty of relieving
you of your weapons.

3
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:11,480
Most of them were government property.

4
00:00:11,980 --> 00:00:15,360
As for the suit, I think you've earned it.

5
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:25,600
The border world, Zen, is in our control
for the time being, thanks to you.

6
00:00:25,601 --> 00:00:29,460
Quite a nasty piece of work you managed
over there.

7
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:31,160
I am impressed.

8
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:40,140
That's why I'm here, Mr. Freeman.

9
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:45,420
I have recommended your services to my...
employers.

10
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:50,200
And they have authorized me to offer you a
job.

11
00:00:50,201 --> 00:00:55,320
They agree with me that you have limitless
potential.

